                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d423">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Sleeper</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-09-14">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 14, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Sleeper says that upon receipt of the cable instructions he immediately
                    requested Captain Colwell, who had already landed force, as per telegram of the
                    13th, to withdraw it.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
